Program: Great Lives
Title: Paavo Nurmi
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b009twrf
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 23 Dec 2016
Series of biographical discussions with Matthew Parris. Former athlete and television commentator Steve Cram nominates Paavo Nurmi, the 'Flying Finn'. Middle and long distance runner Nurmi won nine gold medals in 12 Olympic events and is often considered the greatest track and field athlete of all time. Show less